{{> header title=(concat "Your " brand.displayName " FTTB order")}}

<tr>
  <td style="padding: 20px 15px;">
    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: {{brand.colors.headerText}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          <strong>Let’s get you connected</strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          <strong>Order number:</strong> %%ORDER_NUMBER%%
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          Hi %%NAME%%,
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          It's great to have you on board with {{brand.displayName}} FTTB on the Vision network. Here are the next steps to get you connected to the internet.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: {{brand.colors.headerText}}; padding-bottom: 8px;">
          <strong>Your plan and service</strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          <strong>Your plan is the:</strong> %%PLAN%%
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          Here are some important documents relating to your FTTB service:
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          <a href="%%CRITICAL_INFORMATION_SUMMARY_CIS%%" style="color: {{brand.colors.primary}}; text-decoration: underline;">Critical Information Summary (CIS)</a><br />
          <a href="%%TERMS_NAME%%" style="color: {{brand.colors.primary}}; text-decoration: underline;">Terms and Conditions</a></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: {{brand.colors.headerText}}; padding-bottom: 8px;">
          <strong>Technology Type</strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          <strong>Your Vision technology type is:</strong> Fibre to the Building (FTTB)
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: {{brand.colors.headerText}}; padding-bottom: 8px;">
          <strong>Modem</strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          You can plug in your {{brand.displayName}} modem using our <a href="%%SETUP_GUIDE%%" style="color: {{brand.colors.primary}}; text-decoration: underline;">setup guide</a>.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          If you’re using your own modem, check out our <a href="%%BYO_SETUP_GUIDE%%" style="color: {{brand.colors.primary}}; text-decoration: underline;">BYO setup guide</a>.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: {{brand.colors.headerText}}; padding-bottom: 8px;">
          <strong>Installation Details</strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          Your appointment will be confirmed by email in the next few days.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          <strong>Installation address:</strong> %%INSTALLATION_ADDRESS%%
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          For your upcoming installation, technicians will need to access your premises. They may also need to install new wiring and an internet wall plate. Someone who is 18 years or older will need to be present at the premises for installation.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          Should you have a question about your order, please call us on {{brand.support.phone}} and we’ll be happy to help.
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td style="padding: 20px 15px 60px;">
    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}};">
          Thanks,<br>
          Your {{brand.displayName}} Team
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </td>
</tr>

{{> footer showThingsHeading=true}}
